name: v2.0.0
body:
- implementation of Ratcliff-Obershelp string distance
- bump to Java 8
Re-release, because 1.2.0 messed up and didn't reach maven central...

name: Early termination
body: Levenshtein and WeightedLevenshtein now accept a limit parameter, to allow early termination
WeightedLevenshtein : add possibility to give different weights for characters insertion/removal thanks to PR from ewanmellor

name: v1.0.1
body: Make ShingleBased class public (see issue #39 by @wagjo)

name: v0.24
body:
- removed unused sparse vector classes 
- slightly improved Jaccard index computation

name: v0.23
body: - add QGram.distance(profile1, profile2), to compute distance between precomputed profiles.
- Fix issue #27 (ngram distance with String size < n)

name: v0.20
body:
- Performance improvements: remove unnecessary calls to HashMap.containsKey()
- Added Sift4 algorithm

- cleaned profile based similarities
- fix bug in ngram similarity
Avoid division by 0 when one of the strings has length 0
- fixes int multiplication overflow (with large strings)
Cosine similarity returns 0 if one of the strings is shorter than k (the size of shingles), instead of NaN

name: Refactored to use string profile where applicable (Q-Gram, Cosine, Jaccard and Sorensen-Dice)
Damerau-Levenshtein; Jaccard index; Sorensen-Dice coefficient; Cosine similarity.
